summary: Senators are progressing a House-passed stopgap funding bill, indicating a possible resolution to the ongoing 40-day government shutdown. title: Female NSW MPs Allegra Spender and Kellie Sloane report death and rape threats after condemning neo-Nazi rally in Sydney
